link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28987,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/09\/umar-humility-raises-wisdom\/","url_meta":{"origin":33190,"position":2},"title":"Umar on Humility: Allah raises his wisdom if he humbles himself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ubaydullah ibn \u2018Adi reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said upon the pulpit, \u201cVerily, if a servant humbles himself for Allah Almighty, he will increase his wisdom.\u201d Source: Juz\u2019 fi\u0304hi\u0304 H\u0323adi\u0304th Sufya\u0304n ibn \u2018Uyaynah 24 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19921,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/10\/08\/umar-ask-sheep-euphrates\/","url_meta":{"origin":33190,"position":3},"title":"Umar on Rights: I fear Allah will ask me about my animals","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 8, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Dawud ibn Ali reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cIf a lost sheep under my care were to die on the banks of the Euphrates, I would expect Allah the Exalted to question me about it on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304' 137\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38216,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/09\/08\/umar-control-anger-whims\/","url_meta":{"origin":33190,"position":4},"title":"Umar on Taqwa: Fear Allah, control anger and desires","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 8, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Abdullah al-Khurasani reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cWhoever fears Allah does not vent his anger, and whoever is mindful of Allah does not do whatever he desires.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd li-Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 98 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064f\u0631\u0627\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064f \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064e\u0637\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0628\u0650 \u0631\u0636\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26014,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/04\/big-belly-punishment-not-blessing\/","url_meta":{"origin":33190,"position":5},"title":"Umar on Gluttony: A large belly is a punishment, not a blessing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 4, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Hasan reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, saw a man with a large belly and he said, \u201cWhat is this?\u201d The man said, \u201cI